OL,3,CFirst look at Principality Stadium's
OL,4,Caerial adventure
OL,6,FA zip wire on the roof of the is
OL,7,Fopening to the public on Monday.
OL,9,FThe eagerly anticipated attraction,
OL,10,Fcalled 'Scale', will be open year-
OL,11,Fround at the stadium in Cardiff,
OL,12,Fpotentially on match days in the
OL,13,Ffuture.
OL,15,FSuspended 50 metres above the pitch,
OL,16,Fgetting on the zip wire involves
OL,17,Fclimbing to the top of the
OL,18,FPrincipality Stadium roof, up 15
OL,19,Fflights of stairs.
