OL,3,CFirst look at Principality Stadium's
OL,4,Caerial adventure
OL,6,FIt aims to blend "adrenaline and
OL,7,Fpanoramic views to try to attract a
OL,8,Fbroader audience to the home of Welsh
OL,9,Frugby," according to organisers.
OL,11,F'Scale' is comprised of three parts.
OL,12,FThe first is called 'the climb', which
OL,13,Fas well as involving a lot of stairs,
OL,14,Fincludes walking across the edge of
OL,15,Fthe roof to take in a bird's-eye view
OL,16,Fof the pitch.
OL,18,FThe second part is 'the zip wire',
OL,19,Fwhich travels at about 27 miles per
OL,20,Fhour, and the third is 'the drop',
OL,21,Fwhere people can abseil to the bottom.
