OL,11,FThe organisers are partnering with
OL,12,FWire and Sky, who have worked on
OL,13,Fsimilar projects at Wembley Stadium,
OL,14,FTottenham Hotspur Stadium and
OL,15,FLiverpool FC's Anfield.
OL,17,FViews from the top stretch all the way
OL,18,Fto Cardiff Bay and the iconic
OL,19,FMillennium Centre, as well as many
OL,20,Fother landmarks.
