OL,3,CFirst look at Principality Stadium's
OL,4,Caerial adventure
OL,6,FIt is a plan which has been long in
OL,7,Fthe making, with the idea in various
OL,8,Fforms taking more than 14 years to
OL,9,Fcome to fruition.
OL,11,FTalking to ITV Wales, Scale general
OL,12,Fmanager Claire Jenkins explained:
OL,13,F"It's (the zip wire) taken different
OL,14,Fguises over the years. It was (going
OL,15,Fto be) an internal gantry walk with a
OL,16,Fpop up to the roof and a zip line to
OL,17,Fthe pitch.
OL,19,F"But we needed something we could run
OL,20,Fall the time, while events are going
OL,21,Fon."
